v0.3 released   Feb 28,2015

    *Config stuff moved to QJsonDocument,so code was cleared and improved
    
    *Bug fixed that when scrollbar was scrolled user can not able to select a file or folder.
    
    *System header inclusion removed.Moved from system() to QProcess::startDetached().So platform portability improved.
    
    *Code is public domain from now on. 

v0.2 released   Jan 6,2015

    *Help menu and doc added

    *New feature: Search for pattern in text file and filter files according to result

v0.1 released (first release)   Jan 3,2015